{"tid":752674,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"莎莎女婿陳振邦：努力做嘢可以Full Pay買樓","createTime":"2018-07-23T04:18:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T13:53:14.000Z","uid":55257,"like":4,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bc238cf081d1e263ab441c5611fd6ff7b2a1f761","tid":752674,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T04:18:28.000Z","msg":"樓價癲升，有首期未必過到壓測，要過到壓測就未必夠首期；對於年青人置業難，威威洗衣粉太子爺、莎莎國際（0178）女婿陳振邦就寄語：努力做嘢或者就可以Full Pay買樓上車！<br />\n<br />\n陳振邦接受《明報》訪問時表示，上車夢縱遙不可及，亦不等同要放棄。他建議年輕人先專注工作，等事業有成，或可意想不到地「Full Pay買樓上車」，陳又反駁別人認為他是富二代、「唾手可得」，稱自己落手落腳處理家族生意，幫爸爸做營銷、幫外父睇舖、物色新舖地點；新公司THEBLOCK GROUP改裝工廈工作室的各項事情，自己亦親力親為，「不假手於人」。<br />\n<br />\n陳振邦為威威洗衣粉太子爺，2008年時娶莎莎主席及行政總裁郭少明長女郭詩慧，其後於莎莎任業務發展經理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180723/58475011\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180723%2F58475011&d=aE0a%2F6JPedu4NMNKCVlO2AHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=5049f486\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180723%2F58475011&h=5fd02e96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180723/58475011</a>"},{"pid":"bb07e841be70559b601ee6ecf7fcb580dc0c730a","tid":752674,"uid":42820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T04:21:35.000Z","msg":"係真愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f79b8e9f863398c1f747f83079c48b0dd57a6c","tid":752674,"uid":40397,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T04:26:58.000Z","msg":"佢老豆好野,捱到有間公司,識到D上流人<br />\n等個仔可以嫁入去,然後去埋人地間公司度做野"},{"pid":"83194676eb58f2803281eb800c46ddb6e0ef7de9","tid":752674,"uid":84040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:40:00.000Z","msg":"好叻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bo